{
  "page": "Fire Upon the Grass",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>Fire Upon the Grass</b></i> is a chronicle of <a href=\"/index.php/Terrio_Erastes\" title=\"Terrio Erastes\">Terrio Erastes</a>, the great <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavosi</a> adventurer. He wrote his chronicle during his time amongst the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a>. Being a guest of Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Dhako\" title=\"Dhako\">Dhako</a>, Terrio witnessed the fall of <a href=\"/index.php/Ib\" title=\"Ib\">Ib</a>.  In his chronicle he describes how Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Dhako\" title=\"Dhako\">Dhako</a> and his <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khalasar\" title=\"Khalasar\">khalasar</a></i> were eventually defeated by Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Temmo\" title=\"Temmo\">Temmo</a> in battle.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_ib.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_ib.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fire_Upon_the_Grass&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_ib.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_ib.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Ib.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403110509\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\